{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-detail-tsx","path":"/post-2018-05-18","webpackCompilationHash":"7ffd138fb0c946617a5a","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Silence","author":"默尝"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"644815a2-ee3c-584c-b60f-9834ddae54f6","excerpt":"最近这个记仇图片在我的一些群里出现次数相当高，朋友们都会去用修图软件去改下面的文字，作为一个前端党就在想能不能更加便利一点，一开始想用  去画文字，后来就偶然搜到了 html2canvas，是一款截图工具，那这样就方便多了。  实现  具体实现方式就是利用 html2canvas 对一个 Div…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>最近这个记仇图片在我的一些群里出现次数相当高，朋友们都会去用修图软件去改下面的文字，作为一个前端党就在想能不能更加便利一点，一开始想用 <code class=\"language-text\">canvas</code> 去画文字，后来就偶然搜到了 <a href=\"http://html2canvas.hertzen.com/\">html2canvas</a>，是一款截图工具，那这样就方便多了。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 252px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6ee73319aee69d8768ab119347361f82/2f762/jichou.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 98.01587301587301%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"jichou\"\n        title=\"jichou\"\n        src=\"/static/6ee73319aee69d8768ab119347361f82/2f762/jichou.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6ee73319aee69d8768ab119347361f82/8ee9c/jichou.jpg 148w,\n/static/6ee73319aee69d8768ab119347361f82/2f762/jichou.jpg 252w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 252px) 100vw, 252px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>实现</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 390px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0100f56054f4b2cbe84d5adccdf3f6d6/53d89/anpai.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.8974358974359%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"anpai\"\n        title=\"anpai\"\n        src=\"/static/0100f56054f4b2cbe84d5adccdf3f6d6/53d89/anpai.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0100f56054f4b2cbe84d5adccdf3f6d6/8ee9c/anpai.jpg 148w,\n/static/0100f56054f4b2cbe84d5adccdf3f6d6/ebbe7/anpai.jpg 295w,\n/static/0100f56054f4b2cbe84d5adccdf3f6d6/53d89/anpai.jpg 390w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 390px) 100vw, 390px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>具体实现方式就是利用 html2canvas 对一个 Div 进行截图，在这个 Div 里有记仇的图片和可编辑的文本框，然后再在下面展示并下载下来就阔以了，这部分涉及到了 base64 图片的下载，也是借用了 segmentFault 上 <a href=\"https://segmentfault.com/q/1010000005816241\">大神的代码</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhanghaoqin.life/jichou/\">体验地址</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/MLuminary/subentry/tree/master/%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E4%BB%87%E5%85%88%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%8B%E6%9D%A5\">项目地址</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"今天这个仇先记下来","date":"May 18, 2018"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/今天这个仇先记下来/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/跨域问题总结/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"跨域问题总结","date":"2018-05-19"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/性感慕课在线被爬/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"性感慕课在线被爬","date":"2018-05-02"}}}}}